      "content": "Hey, i need some help ranking three final candidates for a Senior Software Engineer role. They all have the same level of experience and technical stats, so i need an objective look at their profiles to see who might be the best fit for our lead tracks. \n\nHere are the basics for all three:\n- 8 years experience in distributed systems\n- Proficient in C++, Go, and Kubernetes\n- Expertise in microservices architecture\n- Strong record of mentoring junior devs\n\nCan u give me a quick summary of what to look for in a candidate like this for a high-level role? I'll send the specific names and backgrounds in a sec.",
