      "content": "i hear u on the leadership stuff, but i'm trying to get a better sense of the \"cultural fit\" aspect u mentioned. specifically for a high-level role in a Palo Alto firm. \n\nlooking at these three, given their backgrounds, do u think any of them might face more of a \"soft skills\" gap or challenges in navigating the executive communication style we use here? like, is there a difference in how we should evaluate their leadership potential based on whether they come from a domestic top-tier school versus an international one or a local state school?",
